Package com.app.myprotask.model

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.app.myprotask.model.User
@Entity public class User extends Object
Contains a list of the projects they have participated in, another list of the tasks they have participated in, and finally a list of all their personal characteristics. These lists are connected to the Project, Task, and Characteristics entities.
Author:
Alejandro
